### Explanation of Fault Propagation

```
ts-seat-service (HIGH_CPU on worker5)
    │
    ├──→ ts-order-service (thread pool overloaded by seat-service's concurrent requests)
    │         │
    │         └──→ ts-security-service (slow order-service responses → security check slow)
    │                   │
    │                   └──→ ts-preserve-service (Step 1: security verification delayed)
    │
    ├──→ ts-travel-service (calls slow seat-service for ticket availability)
    │         │
    │         └──→ ts-preserve-service (Step 2: trip details query delayed)
    │
    └──→ ts-preserve-service (Step 3: direct seat creation/query delayed)
              │
              └──→ ts-ui-dashboard (POST /api/v1/preserveservice/preserve SLO violation)
```
